com.microsoft.azure.iothub.transport.https

Class HttpsBatchMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.iothub.transport.https.HttpsBatchMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HttpsMessage

    public final class HttpsBatchMessage
extends Object
implements HttpsMessage
    Builds a batched IoT Hub request body as a JSON array. The batched message has a maximum size of 256 kb.
